title: Robbery Problems around the SF Bay Area
description:
I was robbed on Treasure Island, San Francisco at dusk on 9/27. My camera, lens and tripod, all gone. Please be careful everyone! It's so terrible around the Bay Area recently. Be sure if you are safe while you are photographing.

This image was taken with cell phone when I was waiting for the police; spot location is looking southwest to the Bay Bridge and downtown of San Francisco from Yerba Buena Island.

9/27 傍晚我在舊金山金銀島的路邊被搶劫了，當我專注於拍照之際，人被推倒於地，相機瞬間被搶走，包含相機、鏡頭、濾鏡與三腳架，前後僅只 3、4 秒鐘而已。大家請注意安全，出門拍照千萬別一個人落單獨行，舊金山灣區最近搶風非常非常猖狂。
